 Renowned Nigerian comedian Bovi Ugboma, also known as Bovi, and broadcaster, Layole Oyatogun are the official hosts for the 2019 edition of the Most Beautiful Girl in Nigeria (MBGN) pageant. The prestigious beauty pageant is scheduled to take place in Bayelsa State. All the beautiful 37 contestants are ready to storm the Gabriel Okara Cultural Centre, Yenagoa, on Friday Oct 11 2019 in  grand style, as they showcase their beauty and talent to the world. The post Bovi & Layole Oyatogun to Host MBGN 2019 appeared first on BellaNaija – Showcasing Africa to the world. Read today!. Source: Bella Naija